description: Elder Lindsay (Garret Cooper) and Elder Ricci (Mike Edge) had a long day of knocking on doors, but Elder Lindsay can’t stop fantasizing about his companion. When they get back to their apartment, they plop down on Elder Ricci’s bed to discuss their day. Elder Ricci has no idea what’s in store for him, but Elder Lindsay is determined to get into the other boy’s pants.
title: Elder Lindsay: Companionship Inventory RAW
